name: Backtrack: The Jellyfish Heist
description:
Oh no! The jellyfish have had their gold stolen by the evil sea creatures! There's only one option: Steal it back! #jellyfishheist
  • Play as 50 unique jellyfish with unique abilities and stories
  • Explore 3 underwater kingdoms, each with their own crazy fish boss
  • Get really rich
  • Profit $$$$$$$$$$$
